Rules:
    # Init stuff
    - init-publisher if !publisher.exist() => publisher.init() 
        if msg == '' => send(msg); msg = ''
    - init-listiner if !listiner.exist() => listiner.init() 
        if something in topic/turtlesim/Pose => set_data()

    
    # Do Stuff
    - move-to-target if pos != target.pos => move-to-target() wait()
        2. calc distance to target
        3. if distance > margin && speed > 0 => continue 
            else if distance > margin && speed == 0 => calc heading and move.
    - get-new-target if pos == target.pos => target = target.next()

    
    # Functions
    - Send() get publisher, send to topic/turtlesim/Pose